--- 
 <div class="w-full">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8 xl:px-4">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end md:gap-10 mb-4 md:mb-20"
    >
      <div class="w-full md:w-7/12">
        <h4 class="uppercase text-[14px] text-[#F58220] mb-4">Fund</h4>
         <h2
        class="text-[28px] md:text-[35px] md:text-4xl font-heading leading-[120%] mb-8 gradient-text w-full"
      >
      One connected platform for every fund workflow
      </h2>
       <p data-reveal class="fade-up font-normal mb-3 w-full">
        Fund is a comprehensive platform built to manage the full lifecycle of Alternative Investment Funds (AIFs). From fund structuring to NAV computation and reporting, it provides a single, integrated system that ensures accuracy, compliance, and operational efficiency. 
</p>
<p class="mb-3">The platform has two core modules:</p>
<ul class="ml-6">
  <li class="mb-3 list-disc">
    Fund Management (Upstream): Configure fund structures, legal and regulatory data, and key documents with governance controls.
  </li>
  <li class="list-disc">Fund Accounting (Downstream): Automate NAV calculations, contribution tracking, distributions, and reporting â€” ensuring audit-ready accuracy and full transparency.</li>
</ul>
      </div>
